= SDL_TextureModulate =
The texture channel modulation used in [[SDL_RenderCopy]]().


== Values ==
{|
|SDL_TEXTUREMODULATE_NONE = 0x00000000
|no modulation
|-
|SDL_TEXTUREMODULATE_COLOR = 0x00000001
|srcC = srcC * color
|-
|SDL_TEXTUREMODULATE_ALPHA = 0x00000002
|srcA = srcA * alpha
|}

